                      <aside class="sidebar col-12">
              <div class="widget post_end_points-2 widget_end_points"><h4 class="h2 mb-20 text-uppercase">End Points</h4>			<ul>
									<li>As we emerge from COVID-19, we are discovering that the speed and distance of change are having a ripple effect on human work.</li>
									<li>With organizations and workers becoming more fluid, leaders must think about cyber risk in new ways.</li>
									<li>Next-generation enterprise cybersecurity needs to meet a constantly changing landscape of workers, tasks, roles, resources and geographical locations. </li>
							</ul>
</div><div class="widget post_topics-2 widget_post_topics"></div><div class="widget banner-3 widget_banner">		<!-- <div class="mboxDefault"></div>
		<script>mboxCreate('srt-banner-right','param1=value1','param2=value2');</script> -->

